will increasingly be running on multiple networks as a result the industry needs a more integrated solution to combine activation and synch technology with smarter connectivity in addition to moving away from standalone software that needs to be installed and tested the integration of smartmobility with our convergencenow plus  platform creates a standardized way to service the industry which benefits both enterprises and consumers by eliminating redundancies reducing costs and streamlining faster product introductions” waldis added “we are partnering with a tier one service provider as well as some original equipment manufacturers oems to roll out our smartmobility product we currently anticipate moving into production in late  with additional functionality and partners being launched in ” “we are very excited to be a part of the synchronoss family” said biju nair president  ceo of sapience “the addition of smartmobility to synchronoss’ convergencenow plus platform creates a new paradigm in mobility management that costeffectively improves timetomarket and enables new revenue streams for our customers” if you liked this article you might like synchronoss shares spike on strategic review as buyout shop activist hovers the cloud computing companys move comes after siris capital acquired a  stake in may and had been pushing to buy the business ronald orol jul    am edt sp  snaps threeday decline crude comes off highs stocks turn mixed in final hour crude comes off highs keris alison lahiff jun    pm edt stocks mixed russell  leads on reconstitution day stocks trade mixed as crude oil rises after falling earlier in the session keris alison lahiff jun    pm edt stocks maintain gains sp  on track for slight weekly increase stocks turn higher as crude oil rises after falling earlier in the session keris alison lahiff jun    am edt trending walmart in focus amid horrific human trafficking incident in texas that causes nine deaths we must all stop blindly trusting in the ap